public void setShowOn(Device device)
Sets the kind of device, this widget is shown on.

The widget is not shown on any other device.

Only works if responsive design is turned on!

setShowOn

@Deprecated
public void setShowOn(String device)
Deprecated. This Method should never be called directly. It will break your implementation if any style names change. The only valid use is inside UiBinder files where it processes the showOn="..." argument. Use setShowOn(Device) instead!
